data.description: Showstopper! Homes are going up everywhere...but land, that is NOT being made anymore. This house has it all! Come make this beauty yours. The perfect place just in time to make all those special memories. This remodeled home is move-in ready! It is a one-story with a perfect 3-2 split bedroom arrangement. The living room has a wood burning fireplace with soaring ceilings leading to the spacious kitchen, and large dining room. An island with plenty of storage and seating. The open concept living is fantastic for entertaining and holidays! The stainless-steel kitchen appliances and W/D new in 2022 will convey if buyer desires. Before you leave check out the oversized insulated 2 car detached garage, with built in dog room.
